cu.explanation_en: Setting the NR cell ID to 100000 exceeds the valid range (0-1007), causing cell identification errors and network registration failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PRACH msg1 frequency start to 100 exceeds the valid range (0-217), leading to improper PRACH configuration and RACH failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PRACH msg1 頻率起始設定為 100 超過有效範圍 (0-217)，導致 PRACH 配置不當，並造成 RACH 失敗。
